### -----------------------------
###  FIGURE & REPORT OUTPUTS

## GIF animations and PNG frame sequences (large media, regenerable from scripts)
*.gif
make-environmental-drivers/GIFs/

## terra scratch dir (init_terra() temp tiles -- .tif/.vrt/.gri, fully disposable)
make-environmental-drivers/terra-temp/

## GIF frame scratch (PNGs encoded into the .gif, then disposable)
gif-frames/

## Monthly TIFF aggregates written by make-gif-videos.R (regenerable)
## Note: var-stack-TIFF and var-stack-NC outputs are also large; NC outputs are
## already excluded by *.nc above -- this includes var-stack-NC-daily/ (~47 GB),
## which is kept locally for possible future use but intentionally never pushed.

